jsx.http.rpc.remote
Class RemoteReflector

java.lang.Object
  js.Disposable
      jsx.http.rpc.HttpRemote
          jsx.http.rpc.XMLHttpRemote
              jsx.http.rpc.remote.Remote
                  jsx.http.rpc.remote.RemoteReflector
Direct Known Subclasses:
Reflector, ServerReflector
public abstract class RemoteReflector
extends Remote

An abstract base class for remote reflect service providers.

Note that a remote reflect service provider is also a Remote object.

Author:
J.J.Liu (Jianjun Liu) at http://www.jscripter.org
